	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On super mario bros 3, there's a game genie code 'AOSUZI' which edits registry B5DA from FF to 10.
<br />
<br />Now when I change the code through a hex editor, I get the exact same spot it was at too, but nothing changes.  Mario doesn't pull blocks out from the background tiles.
<br />
<br />Why is this?

		

		</td>
