	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You should know how the GameGenie works. Anyway, it patches the CPU address, not the ROM offset. So, it's the ROM bank loaded in the $A000-BFFF region.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


